3. Nightveil Prowler (Legendary Dagger)
3.1 Item Definition

Nightveil Prowler
Level 60 · Dagger · Legendary

Stats:

+46 Agility

+36 Stamina

+96 Attack Power

+3% Crit Chance

+1% Hit Chance

Passive — Prowler’s Bleed:

Your attacks from stealth or within 3 seconds of breaking stealth apply Nightveil Bleed:

Moderate bleed over 12 seconds.

Each time you re-apply from stealth, it refreshes and slightly increases damage (stacking up to 3).

Passive — Slip Through Shadows:

When you kill an enemy that grants XP/loot:

Gain +30% movement speed and +10% dodge for 4 seconds.

Internal cooldown: 20 seconds.

This gives rogues/assassins a clear assassin / chain-pull fantasy.

3.2 Acquisition — The Silent Hunt (Dagger Route)

Questline name: “The Silent Hunt: Nightveil”

Structure:

Mark the Prey (stealth challenges on notable elites/rares).

Slay Without Footsteps (timed stealth instances).

The Nightveil Prowler (final assassination scenario).

Step 1 — Mark the Prey

Objectives:

Use Nightveil Mark item from a rogue NPC to mark:

Mossfur Gnarlbear (Greatwood)

Basalt Juggernaut (Ashen Ridge)

Frostvein Colossus (Frostmarch)

Shade Sovereign (Duskhollow)

Conditions:

Must be in stealth when applying the mark.

Must contribute significant damage during fight (prevent tag/AFK cheese).

Rewards:

Each kill drops:

Marked Gnarlbear Fang

Marked Basalt Core

Marked Frostvein Shard

Marked Sovereign Shadow

Turn in to Shadeblade Elaris (rogue mentor).

Reward:

“Unfinished Nightveil Blade” (cosmetic dagger, not equippable).

Next quest.

Step 2 — Slay Without Footsteps

Three stealth-focused mini-scenarios:

Greatwood — “Whisper in the Grove”

Infiltrate a camp without being detected more than X times; assassinate a lieutenant.

Ashen Ridge — “Cinders in the Dark”

Navigate a lava forge area, using timing and shadow cover to kill a target.

Duskhollow — “Moonless Shadows”

Move through a heavily-patrolled ritual circle; kill the ritualist without triggering a full alarm.

Completion upgrades:

Unfinished Nightveil Blade → Tempered Nightveil Blade

Step 3 — The Nightveil Prowler (Instance)

Instance: “The Silent Court”

A ritual court of shadow nobles / void creatures.

Objective: Assassinate the Nightveil Regent.

Mechanics:

Heavy emphasis on stealth phases:

If you brute-force too much, fails or becomes heavily difficult.

Final blow must be by you while in stealth (or just after exiting).

Success completes the ritual and stabilizes the dagger.

Reward:

You receive Nightveil Prowler (Legendary dagger).

Tempered blade is consumed.

3.3 Quest Skeleton (Lua)
Quests["LEGENDARIES.NIGHTVEIL_PROWLER"] = {
